OL,6,FThe offence took place between
OL,7,FNovember 2021 and February 2022, when
OL,8,Fshe willfully received a quantity of
OL,9,Fclass A drugs, namely cocaine,
OL,10,Freceived a sum of money to convey the
OL,11,Fdrugs into HMP Parc in Bridgend, and
OL,12,Freceived a package containing illicit
OL,13,Fitems to convey into prison.
OL,15,FThe former prison officer, of Birch
OL,16,FGrove, Llanharry, near , also pleaded
OL,17,Fguilty to possession with intent to
OL,18,Fsupply cocaine, possession with intent
OL,19,Fto supply cannabis, and possession
OL,20,Fwith intent to supply buprenorphine.
