OL,6,FDefence barrister Owen Williams said
OL,7,Fthe offences took place at a time when
OL,8,Fhis client was suffering with mental
OL,9,Finstability and an addiction to drugs.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police said Beer was
OL,12,Farrested in the prison car park in
OL,13,FFebruary 2022 and resigned from her
OL,14,Frole following the charges.
